        <item>
            <title>微软 Copilot Search 挑战 Google 搜寻地位，引入 AI 互动助用户延伸搜寻</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-copilot-search/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-copilot-search</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/05/microsoft-copilot-search/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 05 Apr 2025 03:00:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[microsoft]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Search Engine]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1301697</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="flex flex-1 grow basis-auto flex-col overflow-hidden"><div class="relative h-full"><div class="flex h-full flex-col overflow-y-auto [scrollbar-gutter:stable]"><div class="@thread-xl/thread:pt-header-height mt-1.5 flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="text-token-text-primary w-full" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-6" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto py-5 px-6"><div class="mx-auto flex flex-1 text-base gap-4 md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden" tabindex="-1"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn @xs/thread:px-0 @sm/thread:px-1.5 @md/thread:px-4"><div class="relative flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="17613ce9-30aa-4a8e-be9b-7c3bba15671e" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full break-words dark"><p class="" data-start="103" data-end="269">Microsoft, 微软正式在 Bing 搜寻中引入全新 AI 搜寻介面 Copilot Search，用户可透过 bing.com/copilotsearch 使用，获得由人工智能生成的答案，并即时展开延伸提问或深入阅读资料来源。这项设计与 Google 近期为搜寻引擎引入的 AI 模式互相呼应。</p><p data-start="103" data-end="269"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1301704" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1-617x580.jpg" alt="" width="617" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1-617x580.jpg 617w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/copilotsearchonbing1.jpg 957w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 617px" /></p><p class="" data-start="271" data-end="397">Copilot Search 介面以简洁首页展示示范提问及搜寻栏，用户输入查询后，系统会汇整多个网上资料来源，产出 AI 回应，结果页会出现「查看所有连结」与「查看推理」两个按钮。</p><p class="" data-start="503" data-end="616">针对偏好传统网页连结版面的使用者，Bing 仍保留原有搜寻功能。在自然语言提问时，搜寻结果页上方会显示名为 Copilot Answer 的段落，以 AI 模式快速呈现重点资讯，下方则列出常规网页连结，提供一种混合式搜寻体验。</p></div><p data-start="503" data-end="616">来源： <a href="https://dig.watch/updates/ai-powered-search-expands-with-microsofts-copilot-search">dig.watch</a></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
